➜福建新店新车！福建首批“BEIJING汽车”全新品牌形象店开业
http://www.sohu.com/a/430870909_99994080	28778
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201110/612571960f914f3a8651f348d7aea8f9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201110/a94fb305297e49fe8f5cd9fbd1b9d875.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>本文编辑：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201110/f32530bf78c24912935df85267d5222e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>写在前面：</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
